Syntax : restore <player/mob> <full | partial>


  A partial restore will restore all hit points, mana and movement to mortals.
A full restore will restore all limbs, and cure the mortal of all diseases.
If used on an immortal, it will reset certain values to their default numbers.
Indiscriminate use of this in the mortal realm is illegal.  Do not restore
mobs or players without GOOD reason. 
